RenameConfig.description:
Configuration for the rename-column action.

# JSON config

```json
{
  "mapping": {
    "first_name": "given_name",
    "last_name": "surname"
  }
}
```

| Field     | Type                    | Description                               |
|-----------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| `mapping` | `{ from: to, … }`       | Dictionary of source → target column names |
